  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Toss the almonds and apricots in a bowl with a pinch of sea salt and roast in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine the mascarpone cheese, goji berries, honey, Argentinian spice blend, and vanilla extract. Blend until smooth.",
    "Add the roasted almonds and apricots to the mascarpone mixture and blend until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a Korean brass bowl and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "If desired, top with coconut flakes, almond flour, dark chocolate chips, or candy pieces before serving.",
    "Refrigerate for an additional 10-15 minutes to allow the toppings to set.",
    "Serve chilled and enjoy!"
  ],
